# Obsidian Rules

## Vault Root
- Open `knowledgeos/` as the Obsidian vault root.
- Keep `.obsidian/` placeholders Git-friendly.

## Linking & Graph
- Use wikilinks, not bare URLs, for internal notes.
- Maintain Related Notes on durable content.
- Dashboards stay thin; indexes hold registries.

## Plugins (Recommended)
Dataview, Tasks, Templater, Git, Kanban, Homepage, Excalidraw, Metadata Menu, Calendar, Style Settings.

## Daily Notes
- Path: `21-Daily-Notes/Journal/`
- Template: [[Daily Note Template]]
- Promote durable outcomes out of daily notes quickly.
